Titolo: Saori (video game)

Anno: 1991

Descrizione: Saori: The House of Beautiful Girls (沙織 -美少女達の館-, Saori: Bishōjo-tachi no Yakata) is an adult-themed adventure video game released in Japan on October 18, 1991 by FairyTale under the name X-Shitei. A controversial event related to the game resulted in the establishment of the Ethics Organization of Computer Software (EOCS). The incident changed the Japanese bishōjo game industry and few games such as Rance remained popular.